cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.CY, cs.EDU 

The paper proposes a deep learning algorithm for student performance prediction, which falls under the category of machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves natural language processing (NLP) techniques to process the textual data, which suggests cs.CL (Computation and Language) as another possible sub-category. Additionally, the paper deals with educational data mining, which could fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society) and cs.EDU (Education).
